recipe.label: Homemade Spicy Sausage and Ricotta Pizza Recipe
Greek Pizza
ingredientLines: 1 tablespoon corn syrup or king syrup or honey or molasses or 1 teaspoon sugar
1 1/2 cups bread flour or all-purpose flour
1/4 cup frozen spinach , defrosted and drained
1 tablespoon olive oil or vegetable oil
2 cups shredded mozzarella cheese or sliced mozzarella cheese , to cover pizza (my personal favorite)
3 slices onions , cut in half and divided into rings, thin slices
1/4-1/2 cup crumbled feta cheese with garlic and herbs
1/4-1/2 cup alfredo sauce (enough to cover pizza)
